        <ArticleTitle>Intracellular parasitism, the driving force of evolution of Legionella pneumophila and the genus Legionella.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>394</StartPage>
          <EndPage>402</EndPage>
          <MedlinePgn>394-402</MedlinePgn>
